sources.title: 1934 Eine Siebzehnjährige ( Alfred Abel, Max Gülstorff)
sources.description: Film aus dem deutschen dritten Reich von 1934. Eine Siebzehnjährige.  U.a mit Alfred Abel und Max Gülstorff

metadata.Plot: Walter is in love with the 17-year-old Erika, but she raves for older, experienced men. When Walter and Erika visit his parents' estate after passing their exams, Erika shows increasing interest in Walter's father, Werner von Schlettow.
metadata.Writer: Max Dreyer, Karl Peter Gillmann, Charlotte Serda
metadata.Actors: Max Gülstorff, Alfred Abel, Franziska Kinz
